call yourselves "we."

287
00:19:54,234 --> 00:19:55,068
Wait.

288
00:19:56,528 --> 00:20:00,157
Then when we went
to that tteokbokki place…

289
00:20:04,411 --> 00:20:06,371
Was this you?

290
00:20:06,455 --> 00:20:07,331
Hey.

291
00:20:08,457 --> 00:20:10,417
EUN-HA, TAE-JEONG

