00:27:18,011 --> 00:27:19,971
They went on a trip,

395
00:27:20,055 --> 00:27:23,016
ate some tangerines, watched some TV,

396
00:27:23,099 --> 00:27:26,102
played Patty Cake, and had a load of fun.

